      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk or anything. like just a small glass of white wine to take the edge off? i feel like it would just make the medicine work a bit smoother since they both help with relaxation. is there really a big difference between a tiny bit and just taking the pill alone?",
